The paper deals with a database search problem and proposes a probabilistic model using relational logistic regression to find the best record(s) for a given query. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
